author: Jonathan Sawyer
title: Gucci Mane Just Dropped a Surprise EP ‘3 For Free’
text:
Share Tweet Email WhatsApp Comments 
Guwop really never stops working. Just a short time after announcing his upcoming album, Drop Top Wizop — a play on the standout line from Migos’ smash hit , “Bad and Boujee” — Gucci Mane has released yet another new project, dubbed 3 For Free . 
As you can probably guess by the EP’s title, the compilation boasts three songs, all of which note production from Atlanta legend, Shawty Redd. 
You can stream 3 For Free below, and be sure to stay tuned for more surrounding Gucci’s forthcoming Drop Top Wizop album.
